column6: NAMOR GOES TO HELL, part 2 of 3! Lost in an arid desert, Namor seeks an escape from the underworld -- while events spiral out of control in New Atlantis. Namor's only hope: one determined young X-Man -- and the man called DOCTOR DOOM!
column8: | writer:Stuart Moore | penciller (cover):Phil Noto | penciller:Ariel Olivetti | editor:Jeanine Schaefer
